OL,3,CWest Yorkshire Police investigate Tory
OL,4,Cdonor over Diane Abbott remarks
OL,6,FWest Yorkshire Police has launched an
OL,7,Finvestigation into alleged racist
OL,8,Fcomments made by Conservative Party
OL,9,Fdonor Frank Hester about MP Diane
OL,10,FAbbott.
OL,12,FIn remarks first reported by The
OL,13,FGuardian, Mr Hester said the Hackney
OL,14,FMP made him "want to hate all black
OL,15,Fwomen".
OL,17,F"I don't hate all black women at all,
OL,18,Fbut I think she should be shot," he
OL,19,Fallegedly said.
