OL,3,CWest Yorkshire Police investigate Tory
OL,4,Cdonor over Diane Abbott remarks
OL,6,FThe alleged remarks were said to have
OL,7,Fbeen made during a meeting at Mr
OL,8,FHester's company the Phoenix
OL,9,FPartnership (TPP) in Leeds in 2019.
OL,11,FAfter the comments were reported, Mr
OL,12,FHester ` the Tory Party's biggest
OL,13,Fdonor ` released a statement admitting
OL,14,Fhe had been "rude" about Ms Abbot but
OL,15,Fsaid his criticism had "nothing to do
OL,16,Fwith her gender nor colour of skin".
OL,18,FOn Friday, 22 March, West Yorkshire
OL,19,FPolice said it was "investigating
OL,20,Fracist comments which were allegedly
OL,21,Fmade at a meeting in Leeds in 2019".
