OL,6,FThe force said it had taken over the
OL,7,Finvestigation from the Metropolitan
OL,8,FPolice Service's Parliamentary and
OL,9,FInvestigation Team, which had
OL,10,Foriginally been contacted about Mr
OL,11,FHester's alleged remarks.
OL,13,F"This is the first time the comments
OL,14,Fhad been brought to the attention of
OL,15,Fpolice" West Yorkshire Police said in
OL,16,Fa statement.
OL,18,FIt added: "Our officers have since
OL,19,Fbeen working to establish the facts
OL,20,Fand to ultimately ascertain whether a
OL,21,Fcrime has been committed.
