OL,6,F"We recognise the strong reaction to
OL,7,Fthese allegations and appreciate
OL,8,Feveryone who has contacted us since
OL,9,Fthe article was published.
OL,11,F"As we continue our inquiry, we are
OL,12,Fkeen to hear from anyone who could
OL,13,Fdirectly assist our investigation."
OL,15,FHaving initially stopped short of
OL,16,Fcalling the alleged comments racist,
OL,17,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak has since
OL,18,Flabelled them as such.
